    "title": "CBI Strikes 80 Locations Across 16 States in the Largest Digital Arrest Raid Yet",
    "summary": "Operation Chakra-VI deployed 60 special teams across 16 states on June 25, 2026, arresting two key operatives linked to a digital arrest network tied to over 200 cases. The scammers used a fake Supreme Court website with forged court orders to extort victims under 'digital arrest.'",
    "category": "India",
