    "publishedAt": "2026-05-15T10:00:00Z",
    "readTime": 3,
    "hero": "/images/stories/india-digital-regulation-offensive-2026-dpdp-it-rules-crypto.jpg",
    "caption": "North Block, Secretariat Building, New Delhi — seat of India's key regulatory ministries driving the 2026 digital regulatory offensive",
